ি দান করলেন তাদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_076_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62570,"position":3,"arabic":"مِّن","translation":"থেকে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_076_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62571,"position":4,"arabic":"فَضْلِهِۦ","translation":"অনুগ্রহ তাঁর","audioUrl":"wbw/009_076_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62572,"position":5,"arabic":"بَخِلُوا۟","translation":"তারা কৃপণতা করলো","audioUrl":"wbw/009_076_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62573,"position":6,"arabic":"بِهِۦ","translation":"সাথে তার","audioUrl":"wbw/009_076_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62574,"position":7,"arabic":"وَتَوَلَّوا۟","translation":"ও তারা বিমুখ হলো","audioUrl":"wbw/009_076_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62575,"position":8,"arabic":"وَّهُم","translation":"এমতাবস্হায় যে তারা","audioUrl":"wbw/009_076_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62576,"position":9,"arabic":"مُّعْرِضُونَ","translation":"বিরুদ্ধভাবাপন্ন (হয়ে গেলো)","audioUrl":"wbw/009_076_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62577,"position":10,"arabic":"٧٦","translation":"(৭৬)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":77,"arabic":"فَأَعْقَبَهُمْ نِفَاقًۭا فِى قُلُوبِهِمْ إِلَىٰ يَوْمِ يَلْقَوْنَهُۥ بِمَآ أَخْلَفُوا۟ ٱللَّهَ مَا وَعَدُوهُ وَبِمَا كَانُوا۟ يَكْذِبُونَ","translation":"whereupon He causes hypocrisy to take root in their hearts, [therein to remain] until the Day on which they shall meet Him\" - because they have failed to fulfil the vow which they had made unto God, and because they were wont to lie.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1312.mp3","surahId":9,"words":[{"id":63168,"position":1,"arabic":"فَأَعْقَبَهُمْ","translation":"তাই তিনি সাজা দিলেন তাদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_077_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":63169,"position":2,"arabic":"نِفَاقًۭا","translation":"মুনাফেকী (দিয়ে)","audioUrl":"wbw/009_077_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":63170,"position":3,"arabic":"فِى","translation":"মধ্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_077_003.mp3","cha